JOBOS AND SALINAS BESS MONTHLY PAYMENT CALCULATION SYSTEM
================================

This program calculates the monthly payment for a solar facility using
interval-level production, irradiance, and inverter availability data.
The workflow is organized into three phases: Input, Calculations, and Output.

--------------------------------------------------
1. INPUT PHASE
--------------------------------------------------

Input Files
-----------
The system requires three input datasets:

Validation
----------
Before processing begins, the program verifies that all required input files
exist. If any file is missing, execution stops immediately with a clear error
message indicating the expected file path.


Data Loading
------------
